  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to correlate phenotype and genotype of Down syndrome patients in
      order to identify the biochemical reactions involved in their mental retardation and their
      other phenotypic characteristics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
